flowchart LR
    EXT[account_statement<br/>release_report/bank_report] --> SPLIT{classificacao diaria}

    SPLIT --> APIB[Baixa API do dia<br/>soma net_amount<br/>payments liquidados<br/>money_release_date = dia]
    SPLIT --> LEG[Ajustes legado do dia<br/>refund + mediation + reserve<br/>shipping + payout + non-sale]

    APIB --> MODEL[Modelo do dia]
    LEG --> MODEL
    MODEL --> EQ{extrato_total_dia<br/>== APIB + LEG }
    EQ -->|sim| OK[Fechamento diario OK]
    EQ -->|nao| GAP[Investigar divergencia]
